    <rigor-hint>FULL</rigor-hint>
    <rigor-reason>Binding constraint change in `.claude/constraints/bff-extensions.md` — must be precise; also touches `.claude/` which mandates main-session. Step 9.5 code-review + adr-check mandatory per CLAUDE.md §8 (binding rule addition; `.claude/` path; tags include `governance`).</rigor-reason>
    <parallel-group>P5-main-seq</parallel-group>
    <parallel-safe>false</parallel-safe>
